(481, 5, '380', '', 'A general store with a conscience.', 'The Elora Mercantile is your local purveyors of fine foods and goods. We support all things local and small producers wherever possible, striving to use local ingredients in our kitchen as much as possible. We change up our offerings regularly to ensure they are seasonally based and rich with exceptional taste and freshness. Must taste items include mini duck wontons, cretons, onion confit, and duck and porc rillettes.\n \n\n A unique experience, all our products are packed in reusable glass jars, as we strive to keep our plastic use to a minimum. Pick up cheese and charcuterie boards, as well as picnic baskets to go, filled with our many in-house treats that will surprise and delight the palate.  \n \n\n We are open for business Thursday to Saturday 11am-5pm, and Sunday 11am-4pm for in store shopping, delivery and curb side pickup.', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"', 1, '2021-06-14', '2021-06-14', 1, '2021-06-14 16:13:03', '2021-06-14 16:13:03', 0, ''),
