(546, 5, '554', '', 'Premium quality unique clothing and footwear right to your doorstep.', 'At Market Co Guelph, we provide you with an excellent shopping experience as our clients’ satisfaction matters a lot.  We have the perfect combination of shoes and clothes that are tailored to meet your needs through our standard shopping practice.  Even if you are not sure of what you want, our e-shop has several ways to help you identify your needs. Everything about Market Co Guelph revolves around our commitment to help you look your best and inspire confidence in you.\n\nVisit our shop to get the full experience; sit, sip & shop.  With the addition of our cafe and lounge, customers can have a refreshing drink while browsing our clothing collections and catching up with friends.\n\nWe have a great team and aim to grow our business more and more, offering our customers the best products available.  We look forward to uniquely outfitting you!', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"', 1, '2021-06-29', '2021-06-29', 1, '2021-06-29 15:31:14', '2021-06-29 15:31:14', 0, ''),
(547, 5, '564', '', 'A Guelph Chiropractor that Ignites Your Life', 'Are you thriving, or just surviving? Dr. Alyssa Shepherd wants to help ensure that you and your family are getting the most out of life. Discover abundant health with her care and advice! \n\nStep Into Your Power with Dr. Alyssa Shepherd\n\nGuelph Chiropractor Dr. Alyssa Shepherd is a mom who is passionate about providing care for families in Guelph and the surrounding communities. When you visit the office, you will not only receive tailored health care to enhance your well-being in body, mind and spirit, but you will also be given the information and resources you need to make the best decisions for you and your family.\n\nAt the office of Dr. Alyssa Shepherd, you’ll find a relaxed environment where you can voice any questions you might have, receive answers and have your needs holistically and thoroughly addressed.\n\nThe Techniques That Work For You\n\nDr. Alyssa knows that effective health care isn\'t just about your body - it needs to address the entirety of you as a holistic being. With many techniques and tools to work with, Dr. Alyssa works to optimize you as a Whole rather than focusing on one specific part of your health. Her methods include: Webster Technique and Neuro Emotional Technique - both of which she is certified in. Manual and instrument-based adjusting is offered, as well as craniosacral therapy, cranial adjusting Turner style (aka CATS) and acupuncture.\n\nBe Seen, Heard and Listened To\n\nDr. Alyssa believes that every person deserves to have the space to be heard. When you become her patient, she\'ll listen carefully to understand your needs and wants, honoring your unique self. When she asks you, \"How are you?\" you\'ll know that she genuinely means it! With a non-judgmental manner and a sincere care for you and your loved ones, she will tailor her techniques to your preferences and comfort.\n\nLearn About Dr. Alyssa\'s Pregnancy and Birthing Courses\n\nBecoming a mother can be an incredible and empowering experience. Dr. Alyssa wants you to enjoy your pregnancy and look forward with excitement to your baby\'s birth. To help with this she offers several online courses including Birth Bliss, her signature online course, as well as smaller courses in prenatal education, partner preparation for birth support, breech presentation and gentle exercises for a more comfortable pregnancy. One-on-one coaching is also available. \n\n\n\n', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"', 1, '2021-06-29', '2021-06-29', 1, '2021-06-29 16:08:54', '2021-06-29 16:08:54', 0, ''),
(548, 5, '565', '', 'Healing Starts With Helping Hands', 'There are a million reasons why one chooses a career path; I had only one, to help people live a more fulfilled active life through therapeutic touch. Having dealt with numerous sport related injuries myself, and experiencing how I was impacted by these isolated incidences,  I was inspired to pursue massage therapy not only as a career, but to make it part of a lifestyle in an effort to enhance the overall wellness of the lives of my clients and my own.\n\nHaving practiced for over fifteen years, I have focused on such areas as craniosacral therapy, myofascial release, pregnancy massage, sports injury treatment and several other pathologies. Whether it\'s treating clients who suffer from every day symptoms as a result of postural strains or high level professional athletes competing in the NHL or training daily for Olympic competition, I apply the same principles but tailor the treatment to meet each client\'s individual needs. As part of my goal to enhance the overall wellness of the people I work with, I have also helped improve the quality of life for individuals coping with chronic diseases like MS, Parkinson\'s, and arthritis.\n\nBy incorporating massage therapy into my own active lifestyle that includes regular exercise, team sports, spending time in nature, being a Mom, feeding us a balanced diet, and working on maintaining a positive attitude, I lead a healthy lifestyle that keeps me energized and eager to take on each day.', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"', 1, '2021-06-29', '2021-06-29', 1, '2021-06-29 16:13:18', '2021-06-29 16:13:18', 0, ''),
(549, 5, '556', '', 'Brining you really (really) good cheese and more.', 'Downtown Guelph\'s only cheese shop. TOMME Cheese Shop is the the Royal City\'s destination for cheese lovers. We stock cheeses from close to home, across the country, and around the world. Awarded Downtown Guelph\'s Emerging Entrepreneur 2018.', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"', 1, '2021-06-29', '2021-06-29', 1, '2021-06-29 16:14:58', '2021-06-29 16:14:58', 0, ''),
(550, 5, '566', '', 'Get to know your community butcher.', 'Our philosophy in business, as in life, is based on a strong sense of community.  We work and play here.  Dine, shop and are entertained here.  We volunteer, teach, and help bring people together. V aleriote’s Market is an extension of our lives and established to support our community and offer the best products and services we possibly can.\n\nThe Valeriote’s Market we know today is a reincarnation of Valeriote’s Groceteria, established in 1910 by Michael Valeriote on Alice Street in the ward.  After operating successfully for over 50 years, the store was sold and eventually converted into housing.\n\nFast forward to 2009, when local businessman Larry Valeriote saw an opportunity to purchase a thriving butcher shop on Yorkshire Street.  Renaming the store Valeriote’s Market, Larry soon after expanded the store to include a full kitchen for prepared meals and baked goods. In 2012, Larry brought chefs Brian Schmeler and Stacey Kanelos onboard, who would subsequently purchase the store in 2019.\n\nWe’re fortunate to have some of the best farmers and producers in the country, and we’re proud to bring their food to your table.  We strive to make these products accessible and affordable, and maybe change the way you eat!', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"', 1, '2021-06-29', '2021-06-29', 1, '2021-06-29 16:21:24', '2021-06-29 16:21:24', 0, ''),
(551, 5, '567', '', 'Olive Oil & Balsamic Vinegar Tasting Bar', 'Owners Claire and Rick Zuccato are incredibly passionate about their high quality Olive Oils and Balsamic Vinegars. The taste, quality, purity, freshness and selection are second to none!\n\nThey proudly bring only the best possible products to their customers in a relaxed, inviting, and comfortable environment with easy access for all.\n\nThe Olive Experience Inc has deep roots in the Guelph community through Claire’s family. The Clair’s came from Ireland in the 1820’s, with Clair Road being named after them. Irene Clair was the youngest daughter that lived on the farm at Clair Road and Gordon. Irene named her eldest daughter “Claire”. The Hanson Expressway is named for Claire’s cousins, the Hanlon’s.\n\nRick’s family has roots in Italy, his father coming from the small town of Bannia, north of Venice.\n\nClaire and I invite you to come in and see what everyone’s talking about! You’ll have fun, and your meals will never be the same again!\n\nRick & Claire Zuccato', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"', 1, '2021-07-06', '2021-07-06', 1, '2021-07-06 12:52:47', '2021-07-06 12:52:47', 1, '10% off any purchase, for Dux Scavenger Hunt participants only!\n\nSimply show us this promo on your phone and we’ll give you a 10% discount on your purchase!'),
(552, 5, '568', '', 'Old world charm.  Modern flair.', 'Located in a 19th Century historical building in downtown Guelph, Atmosphere cafe + etc. offers \"old world charm\" with an impressive modern flair.  The European influenced menu is prepared in our open-concept kitchen with Lunch, Dinner and Late Night offerings.\n\nWe serve over 10 micro-brewed craft beers, an extensive selection of premium wines (featuring 8 by the glass) and a unique selection of innovative martinis.  Other offerings include: Single Malts, Whiskeys, Bourbons, Real Fruit Jambalayas & Specialty Coffees.\n\nInquire about full catering for small to large functions and experience our custom personalized service.', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"', 1, '2021-06-29', '2021-06-29', 1, '2021-06-29 16:51:44', '2021-06-29 16:51:44', 0, ''),
(553, 5, '561', '', 'Get high quality houseplants here.', 'Plant is a houseplant retail store, carrying cacti, succulents, and beautiful tropical foliage.\n\nOur aim is to bring the beauty of greenhouse horticulture together with the convenience of an urban setting, while maintaining responsible environmental and  growing practices. \n\nWe offer pet safe plants, clean air plants, and can also recommend plants for specific environments.', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"', 1, '2021-07-06', '2021-07-06', 1, '2021-07-06 12:55:44', '2021-07-06 12:55:44', 0, ''),
