(606, 31, '1005', '', 'Organic skin treatments you can feel great about.', 'Our Hair Salon Services\n\nOn the hair salon side of our business, we employ a strong team of experienced hairstylists – we are more than confident in being able to deliver beautiful, stunning haircuts and hairstyles to all of our customers.\n\nWe are home to many stylists who have come from varying backgrounds, bringing an exceptional sense of style, definition and elegance to our customers’ hair care needs.  Our talented stylists are available to make your next beauty vision become a reality.  Our salon proudly has vegan color and vegan product options. All of our products are eco-friendly, not tested on animals, and hypoallergenic!\n\n\nOur Esthetics Services\n\nOn the skincare side of our business, we are proud to be partnered with the Eminence organic skin care brand.  Our Eminence skin care products are available to purchase in our salon, or on our skincare website.\n\nWe have recently added the services of a certified oncology esthetician that has designed and modified spa treatments in order to safely and effectively address skin concerns of the cancer patient.  The spa offers premium quality esthetic services within the salon specializing in facials, skin rejuvenation and hair reduction.  Our aesthetician a former skin care, body treatment and waxing instructor at George Brown College, is highly qualified in her field and is dedicated to providing each of her/our clients with an impeccable experience with each visit.', 'Be sure to tell us \"Dux sent me!\"\n\nNOTE:  As this is a \"FreeToBe\" listing, please check in with us prior to visiting, to avoid any disappointments.  Phone is good.  In-person is better.', 1, '2022-01-25', '2022-01-25', 1, '2022-01-25 18:41:27', '2022-01-25 18:41:27', 0, ''),
